---
title: Moroccan Spiced Turkey Bowl with Roasted Vegetable Couscous
description: Our new Moroccan Spiced Turkey Bowl proves that turkey never has to be boring! Served with roasted vegetables mixed with fluffy couscous and a delightfully fresh lemon-mint cream, eating healthy has never been this easy!

